Packages 
Package Description
com.ikalagaming
The root package/namespace for all Ikala classes and packages.
com.ikalagaming.crypto
Provides some useful cryptographic classes and methods.
com.ikalagaming.event
Provides an Event System with systems for handling listeners for and dispatch of events, as well as a base event class.
com.ikalagaming.gui
Common graphical user interfaces that work with the engine.
com.ikalagaming.gui.console
A console for interfacing with the engine, and associated classes.
com.ikalagaming.gui.console.events
Events dispatched by the console.
com.ikalagaming.localization
Handles localization of strings for the engine.
com.ikalagaming.logging
Processes log dispatching for the engine, as well as handling log importance.
com.ikalagaming.logging.events
Events dispatched by the logging system.
com.ikalagaming.packages
Manages packages, which are distinct subsystems of the engine that can be dynamically swapped in and out or enabled/disabled during runtime.
com.ikalagaming.packages.events
Events dispatched by the package system.
com.ikalagaming.packages.rng
A simple random number generator package that should be fairly secure.
com.ikalagaming.permissions
A group-based permissions system.
com.ikalagaming.scripting
Scripting support for the engine.
com.ikalagaming.system
Provides ways of communicating with and controlling the core of the engine (event manager, package manager) using events.
com.ikalagaming.util
Various utility classes that do not fit into other packages.
